{"tid":987920,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有親人中風經驗分享下","createTime":"2019-01-19T16:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T01:05:12.000Z","uid":214074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ec7bbe5ed411a4bda9d573c07f3d7180338f967a","tid":987920,"uid":214074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"大伯前日中風 左腦爆血管<br />\n入醫院做咗緊急手術<br />\n而家仲係ICU昏迷緊<br />\n醫生話右邊身應該會癱<br />\n講野同食野會有困難<br />\n其他狀況要等佢醒返先可以評估到<br />\n有冇人可以分享下 日後復康可以點做<br />\n有冇可能可以康復到同正常人一樣<br />\n成家人都好擔心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601e34fcd27f3669f25fa4d6262b4cd88125b163","tid":987920,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"無 特別上咗年紀"},{"pid":"166a3c829e74fc936293ec65f39c50c34bd32801","tid":987920,"uid":214074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"601e34fcd27f3669f25fa4d6262b4cd88125b163","tid":987920,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:09:30.000Z","msg":"無 特別上咗年紀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:10:11.000Z","msg":"我大伯得40幾歲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a58ec9119e1d1b53ebaa169c3b286b034e41ff3","tid":987920,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:11:05.000Z","msg":"上年有個好錫我嘅鄰居長輩又係爆血管 成塊面出血 醫生做開腦手術但無補於事 之後陷入昏迷 過幾日仲離開埋唉"},{"pid":"338d96319534f89b2c1d683af18b3b92e840ffb6","tid":987920,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"會超辛苦<br />\n自己照顧唔到自己<br />\n除非屋企好有錢<br />\n唔係要其他人放棄份工去照顧佢<br />\n又冇收入"},{"pid":"1987d420c6ee1c6a09188f35bbf50f4c184b228b","tid":987920,"uid":146601,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"阿爺中過風<br />\n之後啲親戚開始買安宮牛黃丸比佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c14ec156724e78c713119e3178e239935619da","tid":987920,"uid":61271,"